      value: question
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8884357301928637071, guid: 00095f5ef19554217ae6d5a81fd425c7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: nodes.Array.data[0].noReply
      value: 'Dhampir: what is this doing here? '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8884357301928637071, guid: 00095f5ef19554217ae6d5a81fd425c7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: nodes.Array.data[1].noReply
      value: "\n "
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8884357301928637071, guid: 00095f5ef19554217ae6d5a81fd425c7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: nodes.Array.data[2].noLabel
      value: put the axe away
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8884357301928637071, guid: 00095f5ef19554217ae6d5a81fd425c7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: nodes.Array.data[2].noReply
      value: 'No i shouldnt do it, i cant do it. my task on this earth is to help....
        no matter the cost. '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8884357301928637071, guid: 00095f5ef19554217ae6d5a81fd425c7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: nodes.Array.data[0].question
      value: You spot a well crafted axe in the far corner of the garden, it looks
        out of place.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8884357301928637071, guid: 00095f5ef19554217ae6d5a81fd425c7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: nodes.Array.data[0].yesLabel
      value: sus
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8884357301928637071, guid: 00095f5ef19554217ae6d5a81fd425c7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: nodes.Array.data[0].yesReply
      value: 'Dhampir: The preist doesn''t look like the type to chop wood... '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8884357301928637071, guid: 00095f5ef19554217ae6d5a81fd425c7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: nodes.Array.data[1].question
      value: the further you look at it the more this axe reminds you of something
        you onc saw in your book, the craftmanship of it seems very reconizable...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8884357301928637071, guid: 00095f5ef19554217ae6d5a81fd425c7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: nodes.Array.data[1].yesReply
      value: ' '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8884357301928637071, guid: 00095f5ef19554217ae6d5a81fd425c7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: nodes.Array.data[2].question
      value: The more you wonder abou this axe, the more dispair seeps into your
        soul... you could end it all right now. no more suffering, no more lies,
        no more pain... only peace...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8884357301928637071, guid: 00095f5ef19554217ae6d5a81fd425c7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: nodes.Array.data[2].yesLabel
      value: Kill yourself
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8884357301928637071, guid: 00095f5ef19554217ae6d5a81fd425c7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: nodes.Array.data[2].yesReply
      value: "You pick the axe up a raises it above your head, you are think about
        your life and all the suffering you\xF8ve had to endure...\n\nDhampir: i
        cant go on lke this.\n\nYou start a count down\n1... you hesitate\n2... is
        this really ahppening\n3... You swing the axe a you h-\n\nRookie: .... What
        are you doing? that seems counter productive... idiot "
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
